title: Ep - 77 - GUS SMYRNIOS FROM FLORIBAMA SHORE
description:
GUS SMYRNIOS FROM FLORIBAMA SHORE 


Kate explains her involvement in a post-reunion Real Housewives of Orange County fight. 


Gus Smyrnios is one of the stars of MTV's new reality TV show "Floribama Shore." The show, set in Panama City Beach, brings together eight strangers. He discusses the reason for joining the show, how the experience has changed his life, and whether he ever envisions working in an office. 


Dr. Carrie Panoff, a Board Certified OB-GYN, reviews TLC’s new series Unexpected, which takes a raw look at three teenage pregnancies and the effects it has on their families as everyone prepares for the arrival of the babies.


Rob Cesternino from Rob Has a Podcast helps Kate review the season premiere of MTV’s Floribama Shore.
